.TH "libnvme_get_attr" 9 "libnvme_get_attr" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_get_attr \- Read sysfs attribute
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "char *" libnvme_get_attr
.BI "(const char *d "  ","
.BI "const char *attr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "d" 12
sysfs directory
.IP "attr" 12
sysfs attribute name
.SH "RETURN"
String with the contents of \fIattr\fP or NULL in case of an empty
value or error.
